<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_a9acb0c48ea5.aspx"><b>鸡鸣</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsona9acb0c48ea5">
<p>鸡既鸣矣，朝既盈矣。匪鸡则鸣，苍蝇之声。<br />东方明矣，朝既昌矣。匪东方则明，月出之光。<br />虫飞薨薨，甘与子同梦。会且归矣，无庶予子憎。</p>
